+# Building InkFrame Studio → APK
+
+InkFrame ships as a single-file PWA (`web/index.html`) wrapped in a thin Android WebView shell. The APK is **debug-signed**, fully offline, sideload-ready.
+
+> APKs from CI, local builds, and GitHub Releases are identical – debug-signed, no Play Store keystore.
+
+Android Studio / SDK is only needed for the APK. The web app runs with zero build tools.
+
+---
+
+## Requirements
+
+| | Version |
+|---|---|
+| Android Studio | Koala (2024.1)+ – bundles JDK 17 |
+| JDK | 17 |
+| Android SDK | Platform API 35, Build-Tools 35.x |
+| Min device | Android 8.0 (API 26)+ |
+
+Pinned in repo: Gradle 8.9, AGP 8.5.2, Kotlin 1.9.24, compileSdk 35.
+
+---
+
+## Quick build – CLI
+
+```bash
+./inkframe-cli build-apk
+# → app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk
+```
+
+Install:
+```bash
+adb install -r app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk
+./inkframe-cli test   # 210 JVM unit tests
+```
+
+---
+
+## Option A – GitHub Actions (no local SDK)
+
+1. Push to GitHub
+2. Actions → **Android CI** → download `inkframe-debug-apk`
+3. Sideload the APK
+
+Release build:
+```bash
+git tag v0.1.0 && git push origin v0.1.0
+# → .github/workflows/release.yml builds InkFrame-v0.1.0-debug.apk
+#   attaches to GitHub Release
+```
+
+---
+
+## Option B – Android Studio
+
+1. File ▸ Open → select repo root
+2. Accept SDK install prompts (API 35)
+3. Run ▶
+4. APK: `app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk`
+
+Gradle JDK must be 17 (Settings ▸ Build Tools ▸ Gradle).
+
+---
+
+## Option C – Command line
+
+```bash
+export ANDROID_HOME=$HOME/Android/Sdk
+echo "sdk.dir=$ANDROID_HOME" > local.properties
+
+java -version   # must say 17
+./gradlew :app:assembleDebug
+```
+
+---
+
+## Sideloading
+
+1. Copy `app-debug.apk` to device
+2. Settings ▸ Security ▸ Install unknown apps → allow your file manager
+3. Tap APK
+
+Debug-signed APKs install without Play Store.
+
+---
+
+## Troubleshooting
+
+| Symptom | Fix |
+|---|---|
+| `Unsupported class file major version` | Use JDK 17 |
+| `SDK location not found` | Create `local.properties` with `sdk.dir=...` |
+| First sync slow | First build fetches AndroidX from Google Maven – needs internet |
+| `Failed to find Build Tools / platform 35` | `sdkmanager "platforms;android-35" "build-tools;35.0.0"` |
+
+---
+
+## Verifying without an APK
+
+```bash
+./gradlew :core-common:test :core-model:test :engine-gl:test
+```
+
+210 unit tests – JSON, GIF/LZW, YUV, HSV, onion-skin, timeline, undo, viewport math.
+
+---
+
+See also: [`PIPELINE.md`](PIPELINE.md) – CLI pipeline, [`RELEASING.md`](RELEASING.md) – release checklist
