+# InkFrame Studio – CLI Pipeline
+
+Unified command-line for InkFrame Studio v5 – Agent Mode ready.
+
+```
+./inkframe-cli <command>
+```
+
+## Local commands
+
+| Command | What |
+|---|---|
+| `dev` | Vite HMR at http://localhost:5173 |
+| `build-web` | `npm run build` → `web/dist/` |
+| `serve` | `python3 -m http.server 8080` |
+| `build-apk` | `./gradlew :app:assembleDebug` |
+| `test` | `./gradlew test` – 210 JVM tests |
+| `bump <patch|minor|major>` | updates `web/metadata.json` + `package.json`, regenerates `RELEASE_NOTES.md` |
+| `release-check` | `node tools/prepare-release.mjs` – prints git tag commands |
+| `export-gif in.inkframe out.gif [--fps 12] [--width 1024]` | Headless GIF via Puppeteer + in-app GifEncoder |
+
+## GitHub / Agent Mode commands
+
+| Command | What |
+|---|---|
+| `gh-clone [dir]` | `gh repo clone artistso/inkframesv5` |
+| `gh-ci [apk|web|test|all]` | Trigger `.github/workflows/agent-build.yml` |
+| `gh-ci-get <run-id>` | Download `inkframe-agent-apk` artifact |
+| `gh-release [patch|minor|major]` | bump → commit → tag → push → CI builds Release APK |
+| `agent build` | test + build-apk (local, CI-free) |
+| `agent web` | npm ci + build |
+| `agent release patch` | full release via gh |
+| `agent export-gif in out` | headless export |
+
+Agent guide: [`../AGENT.md`](../AGENT.md)
+
+## Typical pipelines
+
+**Web dev**
+```
+./inkframe-cli dev
+```
+
+**Android debug**
+```
+./inkframe-cli build-apk
+adb install app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk
+```
+
+**Release (debug APK → GitHub Releases)**
+```
+./inkframe-cli bump patch
+./inkframe-cli release-check
+git tag v0.x.y && git push origin main --tags
+# CI publishes InkFrame-v0.x.y-debug.apk
+```
+
+**Agent Mode – remote build**
+```
+./inkframe-cli gh-ci apk
+gh run watch
+./inkframe-cli gh-ci-get <run-id>
+```
+
+**Batch export**
+```
+./inkframe-cli export-gif my.inkframe out.gif --fps 24 --width 1280
+ffmpeg -i out.gif -movflags +faststart -pix_fmt yuv420p out.mp4
+```
+
+Export needs puppeteer once:
+```
+cd web && npm install puppeteer --save-dev
+```
+
+## CI workflows
+
+- `android.yml` – push/PR: web smoke → unit tests → debug APK artifact
+- `release.yml` – tag `v*`: test → debug APK → GitHub Release
+- `agent-build.yml` – workflow_dispatch: `task=apk|web|test|all`, optional `version_bump`
+
+All three produce the **same debug-signed, fully-wrapped, offline APK**. No Play Store signing, no AAB.
+
+See: `docs/BUILD.md`, `docs/RELEASING.md`, `AGENT.md`
